    "Name": "Bellerophon",
    "Details": "<color=#F79B26>The Bellerophon is a failed prototype that was envisioned to complement the Mackie with its higher speed but lacked stability due to its weapon arrangement.</color>\n\nThe BEL-1X is equipped with a pair of Large Lasers coupled with an SRM-4 which it would use to provide supporting fire for the Mackie. However, both Large Lasers are mounted in the right arm, making it difficult to keep the 'Mech balanced and upright, especially when maneuvering. Furthermore, the Bellerophon's fourteen heat sinks are not enough to offset any heat spikes should the MechWarrior choose to fire all his weapons at once, or even fire the two Large Lasers in tandem.",
